product.title: Micro Cute Little Yidashao Old Street Building Sets
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Build your Little World in the Famous Historical Street in Taiwan

    Taiwan’s old street embodies the atmosphere of once-thriving cities in Taiwan. A number of shops selling vegetables, fruits, and a variety of other necessities are dotted within the narrow streets that formed during the Japanese colonial period. Old Street (Yidashao) is a famous historical street in Taiwan. Built during the Japanese period.

    🌸 Measurements: 4x2x3in / 11x6x6.5cm
    🌸 Not compatible with leading blocks of standard size (16mm) 
    🌸 This is Micro blocks (12mm)
    🌸 Each set has over 500 micro pieces
    🌸 Includes 1 mini doll of each set
    📦 Excludes original box to protect the environment. For further details please see below.*

    We have picked 4 Micro Cute Little Yidashao Old Street for you to build from scratch, role play, and learn how to run a Taiwanese street market in your own room. 

    Little Yidashao Old Street is designed with traditional Taiwanese culture in mind and reveals the strong energy and vitality of the colourful Old Streets. Built with vibrant colored bricks, Little Yidashao Old Street is a dream come true for lovers of Taiwan.

    Please note: All building sets do not come with the original box to protect the environment but they do come in separate bags. For further details please see below.*

    Our first Cute Little Yidashao Old Street sells Taiwanese-Style Steamed Pork Buns. The ubiquitous steamed Taiwanese bread buns stuffed with porky goodness and other heavenly fillings. We normally referred to these steamed buns as “bao” or “bau,” With exquisite details as shown below. It contains steaming hot 154 pieces, measures about 5cm x 10cm.

    Our second Cute Little Yidashao Old Street is a Pawnshop. There was a time when many people were poor and they couldn't afford to buy things. They took these things to a shop called a "Pawnshop." In the Pawnshop, they could get money for their things if they promised to give it back at a certain time. With the exquisite details as shown. It contains cool 557 pieces, measures about 5cm x 9.5cm.

    Our third Cute Little Yidashao Old Street is Kaoliang Wine Store. Open your door to the world of kaoliang wine with our Micro Yidashao Old Street. Kaoliang is a strong distilled liquor of Chinese origin, made from glutinous rice or sorghum with malt and yeast added; it has been used in China for thousands of years. It contains refreshing 582 pieces, measures about 6cm x 10cm.

     

    Our forth Cute Little Yidashao Old Street is Blacksmiths, they would forge many swords for the Palace and swordsman. It contains tough 567 pieces, measures about 5cm x 10cm.

     

    Measurements: allow up to 5cm variations in different sets

    Start building your Taiwanese markets today by following the instruction booklet.

    The perfect gift for those who love their crafts!

    You will love seeing your family and friends in excitement when they receive our micro building blocks, leaving an everlasting smile on your loved ones by surprising them with this super innovative and cool building blocks today.

    Micro Blocks: Smaller than the traditional building block.


    * Our Building Block sets are packaged in safe and secured protective bags. They do NOT come in the original box to reduce the carbon footprint, save the planet and reduce postage cost on your behalf. It will come with all the pieces and a detailed instruction booklet for you to follow along. 

    Features

    🌸 100% premium quality (ABS) plastic
    🌸 Sharp brilliant colors and solid feel
    🌸 Challenging and rewarding to stimulate all brains
    🌸 High-quality durable non-toxic green material

    WARNING: CHOKING HAZARD - Contain small parts; not suitable for children under 6 years old unless there is adult supervision.


  • Do you ship worldwide? Yes, we ship to over 300 countries and proud to provide free shipping to the United States, the United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, and many countries in Europe.

    What are the blocks made from?     All our building blocks are manufactured from a High-Quality Premium strong, resilient plastic known as acrylonitrile butadiene styrene (ABS) and will stand the test of time and provide hours of fun building their own creations

    Does this help with stress and development?     Our building blocks is a great way to relieve stress and engage in meaningful and joyful conversations. As children comment on their building creations, they develop important communication skills including the ability to explain ideas, describe their work, talk about the process and verbalize challenges that they had along the way. 

    CHOKING HAZARD: Small parts. Not for children under 6 years old

     

  • We are proud to offer FREE tracked shipping to over 300 countries worldwide including the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many others. If you are wondering if we ship to your country please head over to our Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
